<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
Add new bugs by editing this page and adding them to the bottom of the list.  Follow the format of the other bugs in the list, please. Developers will move fixed or otherwise resolved bugs to the resolved section of the list. <p>
Only put a summary of the bug on this page.  Write detailed information you have for us on the BugReportN page and tell us about it there.  Mark the bug as a spoiler if the detailed information contains one. 
</p>
<p>
Important: Do NOT write the full bug description onto this page.  Also, never assume the reader of the full Bug Report page has read this page first. 
</p>
<p>
And please, don't bother to recycle bug numbers. There are plenty to go around. 
</p>
<p>
-- <a href="./NeilStevens">NeilStevens</a> 
</p>
<p>
<em>Warning</em>: Many of the links on this page lead to spoily information. Even if the original bug report is not spoily, followup discussion can become so. You have been warned. 
</p>
<p>
-- <a href="./MayLith">MayLith</a> 
</p>
